      "description": "Number of proteins in B but not in A (|B - A|). Represents the uniqueness of B with respect to A. High value = B adds unique coverage beyond A. Zero value = B is completely contained in A (B \u2286 A).",
      "from_schema": "https://ai4curation.io/ai-gene-review",
      "slot_uri": "https://w3id.org/ai4curation/gene_review/b_minus_a_count",
